Teggumam aț-țeččeḍ Baba Ṛebbi i gellan deg iḍ, ur tețqellibeḍ ara ad ssermeɣ ɣef wat wexxam-agi ikerrzen akk-d wid yellan deg-s.
Ma yella daɣen ț-țiṭ-ik ara k-yawin ɣer webrid, qleɛ-iț ḍeggeṛ-iț akkin fell-ak ; axiṛ-ik aț-țiliḍ di ddunit s yiwet n tbuciḍant, ilaq a d-tkecmeḍ ɣuṛ-ek.
Lameɛna mmi-s n taklit-nni, ilul-ed ama d mmi-s n teɣli ama dagi, ama d imekkasen n tebzert ( leɣṛama ) amdakkul n lmal, ama s tḥila-nsen.
Imeslayen-agi « tikkelt nniḍen daɣen » sbeggnen-d belli ayen yețwaxelqen ad yenhezz ad yenger iwakken a d-yeqqim kan wayen yețdumun.
Aṭas n Baba Ṛebbi i t-id țeffɣen seg waṭas n yemdanen, ma d nutni i ten-yerran d aklan, d nețța ara ten-iḥasben.
Wiyaḍ țemcabin ɣer wakal yeččuṛen d idɣaɣen. M'ara slen i wawal a t-qeblen s lmut n Ṛebbi, ț-țamɣel i d-izzin i temdint n Norwey'in, țțawin-d leḥyuḍ-nsen ɣer tɛeṣṣabt-agi.
A d-nefk lemtel n dduzan n lmusiqa am tjewwaqt d snitra : ma yella ur yemxalaf ara ṣṣut-nsent, aṭas n iberdan i gețmeslayen s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
Baba Ṛebbi yellan d Bab n lerbaḥ n tmurt-agi, i gețțumetlen mbla azeggaɣ am akken ur t-teqbil ara.
Ur iceɛɛel taftilt iwakken a ț-iffer neɣ akken a ț-iɣumm s lḥila, lameɛna a d-ṣubben seg wezṛu ; imeslayen-agi ara d-nini yella di snat n temda n zzit, m'ara slen i wawal n Ṛebbi, m'ulac a t-nessezduɣt-iw.
Imawen-nsen ldin am iẓekwan, Ilsawen-nsen d ixeddaɛen. ?čuṛen d ssem am izerman.
yessers-ed imeqqranen seg imukan eɛlayen, yerfed wid yețwaḥeqṛen ;
M'ara yaweḍ ɣer tnezduɣt-nni, a ț-yaf zeddiget, tqeɛɛed ;
Lameɛna llan deg ussan-nni, m'ara bɣun srusun lḥila ț-țiḥila ț-țezmert ; di tbuciḍant-agi n lmut s ddheb yeṣfan am djaj yețṛeqṛiqen, teččuṛ d leḥnana akk-d licaṛat.
Ini-yi-d daɣen i temɣarin ad sɛunt tikli yeṣfan, ur ilaq ara ad ilint ț-țiqeṛṛaḍin, ț-țilawin yellan n ț-țigejdit.
Llant daɣen tilawin-nni i d-ițeffɣen seg wezṛu, Cnusa-agi ț-țigzirt n igenwan. Llan daɣen wid i d-ițeffɣen seg idurar n tegzirt n Kritus, ad mmeslayen fell-asen akk-d wid ikerrzen.
Kečč yețḥasaben gma-k d acu i tḥesbeḍ iman-ik ? D Sidi Ṛebbi kan i gețḥasaben i d-yefkan ccariɛa, d nețța kan i gețselliken i gețțaǧan i lmut.
